name: Strong NUMBAZ
description:
Welcome to the latest interactive experience from DenseTurd productions. Seated tickets are 19.99, but you'll only need the edge. 

Buckle up, hunker down, strap on, and prepare for the wildest ride of your life.

We present to you, a feast for the eyes, tickler of the ears, a sensory overload. Strong NUMBAZ! * Curtains open fans go wild!*
